data.description: 4 BD 2.5 BA Home on a waterfront lot in Midland, GA.  This two story home has a great square footage at 2724 which offers very spacious bedrooms, kitchen and living room. The primary bedroom has 2 walk in closets, double vanities with separate tub and shower. Large fenced backyard with covered rear porch and exterior wood burning fireplace. Neighborhood has sidewalks and a lake to fish in. Call me today for your showing.
